A flexible python tool to create and launch jobs on the cluster and to load the results back into python.

Provides the SimulationJob object

arguments: 
arrayargs	 a dict of parname:[parvalues] of array parameters 
constargs	 a dict of parname:parvalue of constant parameters for all simulations run by the job.

load_data: returns an xarray Data Set with the arrayargs as coordinates (+ specified innner dimension names)	and the constargs as attributes
